OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,FThe vote followed the launch of a
OL,7,Fpolice investigation into Lord
OL,8,FMandelson and concerns about the
OL,9,Fvetting process involved in his
OL,10,Fappointment.
OL,12,FA first tranche of documents, released
OL,13,Fin March, showed Sir Keir Starmer was
OL,14,Fwarned of a "general reputational
OL,15,Frisk" because of Lord Mandelson's
OL,16,Fconnection to the late paedophile
OL,17,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,26,@vD@MOUwD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,FThe second set of documents is
OL,7,Fexpected to include messages between
OL,8,FLord Mandelson and ministers and
OL,9,FGovernment advisers, including Sir
OL,10,FKeir's former chief of staff Morgan
OL,11,FMcSweeney.
OL,13,FFormer health secretary Wes Streeting
OL,14,Fhas already published his own messages
OL,15,Fwith Lord Mandelson, including
OL,16,Fdiscussion of Gaza and criticisms of
OL,17,FSir Keir's leadership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,FBut reports suggest it will not
OL,7,Finclude Lord Mandelson's UK Security
OL,8,FVetting (UKSV) summary after the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police asked the
OL,10,FGovernment to withhold the document to
OL,11,Favoid jeopardising its investigation
OL,12,Finto alleged misconduct in public
OL,13,Foffice by the peer.
OL,15,FUKSV recommended against granting Lord
OL,16,FMandelson security clearance, but top
OL,17,FForeign Office official Sir Olly
OL,18,FRobbins overruled that advice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,FSir Olly was effectively sacked in
OL,7,FApril after it emerged he had
OL,8,Foverruled the advice, with the Prime
OL,9,FMinister insisting he was unaware of
OL,10,FUKSV's recommendation.
OL,12,FThe Government has said it has only
OL,13,Fwithheld documents where requested by
OL,14,Fthe police, and all other documents
OL,15,Fwill be published.
OL,17,FSeveral documents have also been
OL,18,Fredacted, either to remove personal
OL,19,Fdetails such as the names of junior
OL,20,Fofficials, or on national security
OL,21,Fgrounds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
