SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,FRedactions on national security
OL,7,Fgrounds were agreed with Parliament's
OL,8,FIntelligence and Security Committee
OL,9,Ffollowing a compromise with MPs to
OL,10,Fhead off a backbench rebellion on the
OL,11,Fdemand for documents.
OL,13,FLast month, the committee raised
OL,14,Fconcerns that the Government was
OL,15,Fapplying redactions "too broadly", and
OL,16,Fcited the UKSV vetting file as an
OL,17,Fexample of documents being withheld
OL,18,Fwithout Parliament granting ministers
OL,19,Fthe "authority" to do so.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@aO]{D@EOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
