PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,FThe Conservatives have accused the
OL,7,FGovernment of seeking to perpetrate a
OL,8,F"cover-up", with shadow minister Alex
OL,9,FBurghart writing to the chief
OL,10,Fsecretary to the Prime Minister on
OL,11,FSunday to demand "full transparency".
OL,13,FMr Burghart said: "I will remind you
OL,14,Fthat the House did not provide the
OL,15,FGovernment with the choice about
OL,16,Fredactions beyond the narrow scope in
OL,17,Fthe humble address.
OL,19,F"This behaviour will be viewed by the
OL,20,FHouse as a contempt of Parliament, and
OL,21,Fas a cover-up by the British public.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]sD@ROUsD@dO]uD@SOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,F"Even if the Prime Minister leaves
OL,7,Foffice in a few weeks, I can assure
OL,8,Fyou we will hold you to account for
OL,9,Fthis."
OL,11,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,12,Fare committed to complying with the
OL,13,Fhumble address in full.
OL,15,F"The second tranche of documents will
OL,16,Fbe among the largest publications ever
OL,17,Flaid in Parliament.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]sD@aOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1780272174
OL,3,CSecond tranche of Mandelson papers
OL,4,Cexpected to be published
OL,6,F"That reflects the transparent and
OL,7,Fthorough process we have followed, in
OL,8,Fline with established precedent for
OL,9,Fhumble addresses."
OL,11,FOfficials declined to confirm when the
OL,12,Fsecond tranche of documents would be
OL,13,Fpublished.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@RO]
